      "date": "2012-12-07 13:49:38.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/c2355ae6-406b-11e2-8218-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  2 tests failed: replay-single, sanityn.",
