        "username": "liwei",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-12-27 05:35:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nSorry, James, but {get,set}_obdfilter_param() should be renamed to {get,set}_osd_param() instead of {get,set}_ofd_param(), because they are supposed to access OSD parameters that once existed under OBDFilter.  I love the rest of the patch.  Would you consider renaming once more to \"osd\"?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
    },
